# 1. React AGI Governance Hub

## 1.1 Real-Time Risk State Management
The dashboard uses a global `RiskProvider` to propagate safety scores.

```javascript
// Incident Pipeline Hook
const useIncidentTracking = () => {
  const [incidents, setIncidents] = useState([]);

  useEffect(() => {
    const socket = new WebSocket(process.env.KAFKA_TELEMETRY_WS);
    socket.onmessage = (event) => {
      const pulse = JSON.parse(event.data);
      if (pulse.severity >= 3) {
        setIncidents(prev => [pulse, ...prev]);
      }
    };
  }, []);
}
```

## 1.2 SCADA Kinetic Override Component
The UI includes a "Physical Severance" module for Board-level override.
- **Behavior**: Dual-key authentication required.
- **Visual**: A 10-second countdown with rack-level isolation visualization (React rack state component).

## 1.3 PQC WORM Ledger UI
Displays the Merkle-tree validation status for telemetry logs, utilizing Post-Quantum Cryptographic (PQC) signatures to ensure ledger integrity against future compute threats.
